extrasource: I mostly use YouTube to access ABC, FOX and other sites. I also read the a little from the New York Times at times and other sites. I think the first few questions I was thinking it was based on the state winner. I tried to remind myself afterwards it was 100 voters. There were still times I forgot. I tried to think about it being based on 100 voters once I remembered. I still forgot at times. Also, sometimes I think I often did not pay attention to how confident the other person was in their decisions . I think I mostly looked at the decisions in terms of the numbers they chose. I apologize for not paying more attention to how confident they were and for not understanding and at times forgetting the results are based on 100 voters and not the winner of the state.
